{
  "stem": "24409.11",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they addressed me in German.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, I didn't understand a word of German.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I would have made myself suspicious.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "An American who knows German?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Not-- not a [? straight ?] story.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But we found-- we found out that you can communicate because I understand Czech.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was born Prague.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he-- he-- he asked me, what do you want?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Where are you going?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I told him, I am on a confidential mission.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I cannot tell you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he said, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then he came back and said, you are going to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The main general [INAUDIBLE] and to f now in order to negotiate about the entrance of Americans in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, I cannot tell you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He says, I know you are going to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was-- this lieutenant was assigned to accompany us in the jeep to [INAUDIBLE] where the American general was.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There-- [INAUDIBLE] they tried to telephone [INAUDIBLE] but didn't work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The telephone didn't work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And of course, if there was one place I-- one person I didn't want to see was this American general.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then we started drinking, and he became inebriated.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He drank one, and I drank one.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then he drank one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the other one [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There are only two [INAUDIBLE] coming on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] and then he-- he got more inebriated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We didn't drink anymore.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He drank alone.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he told us how beautiful Vienna was and all the experiences which he had with women in Vienna, which has [INAUDIBLE] of women.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I said-- I-- I wouldn't talk [? that time. ?] So directed him to tell me-- to suggest, let's go and see Vienna.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Or maybe I told him, let's go and see Vienna.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He says, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We went to Vienna.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
